---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
import SiteNav from '../components/SiteNav.astro'
---

<BaseLayout
	title="Fabien Brocklesby - Founder of Light Lane"
	description="Fabien Brocklesby is a New Zealand founder and the founder of Light Lane, a company focused on modern software, turnkey business solutions, and broader progress in the laser industry."
	canonical="https://fabienbrocklesby.com/about"
	ogType="profile"
>
	<div class="page">
		<div class="container page-content">
			<!-- =========================================================
           Site Header
           ========================================================= -->
			<header
				class="site-header"
				itemscope
				itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"
				transition:name="site-header"
				transition:persist
			>
				<meta itemprop="name" content="Fabien Brocklesby" />
				<meta itemprop="jobTitle" content="Founder" />
				<meta itemprop="url" content="https://fabienbrocklesby.com" />

				<span class="site-header__eyebrow">Official Site</span>

				<h1 class="site-header__name" itemprop="name">Fabien Brocklesby</h1>

				<p class="site-header__role">
					Founder of
					<a
						href="https://lightlane.app"
						rel="noopener noreferrer"
						target="_blank"
						itemprop="worksFor"
						itemscope
						itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"
					>
						<span itemprop="name">Light Lane</span>
					</a>
				</p>

				<p class="site-header__tagline">
					Modern software and turnkey solutions for the laser industry
				</p>

				<p
					class="site-header__meta"
					itemprop="nationality"
					itemscope
					itemtype="https://schema.org/Country"
				>
					<span itemprop="name">New Zealand</span>
				</p>
			</header>

			<!-- Navigation -->
			<SiteNav activePage="about" />

			<!-- =========================================================
           Page content
           ========================================================= -->
			<main id="main-content" class="page-main" transition:name="page-main">
				<!-- Intro -->
				<section class="section" aria-label="Introduction">
					<p class="intro-text">
						I'm Fabien Brocklesby. I founded Light Lane to change how the laser industry
						works.
					</p>
					<p class="body-text intro-body">
						Light Lane is focused on modern software, turnkey business solutions, and
						the broader systems that determine how laser technology is adopted in the
						real world. I started it because the existing tools and workflows felt
						outdated, fragmented, and far below what modern businesses and creators
						should expect.
					</p>
				</section>

				<!-- What Light Lane is -->
				<section class="section" aria-label="About Light Lane">
					<h2 class="section-label">Light Lane</h2>
					<p class="body-text">
						Light Lane is building the software, the business infrastructure, and the
						longer-term thinking needed to modernise how laser technology reaches the
						world. This is not a single product - it is a serious, long-term effort to
						raise the standard of the industry.
					</p>
					<ul class="focus-list focus-list--spaced">
						<li>Modern laser software</li>
						<li>Turnkey business solutions</li>
						<li>Practical adoption in real workflows</li>
						<li>A serious long-term vision for the laser industry</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<!-- Current Focus -->
				<section class="section" aria-label="Current focus">
					<h2 class="section-label">Current Focus</h2>
					<ul class="focus-list">
						<li>Building Light Lane</li>
						<li>Product and workflow design</li>
						<li>Turnkey laser business solutions</li>
						<li>Real-world adoption across creators, schools, and businesses</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<!-- Official bio -->
				<section class="section" aria-label="Official biography">
					<h2 class="section-label">Bio</h2>
					<p class="bio-text">
						Fabien Brocklesby is a New Zealand founder and the founder of Light Lane. He
						started the company after observing how outdated and fragmented the laser
						industry still was - from the software layer through to how businesses
						actually adopt the technology. His work spans modern laser software, turnkey
						business infrastructure, and a broader vision for making laser technology
						more commercially powerful, more accessible, and more standard across
						real-world use.
					</p>
				</section>
			</main>

			<!-- Footer -->
			<footer class="site-footer" transition:name="site-footer" transition:persist>
				<div class="site-footer__inner">
					<p class="site-footer__copy">&copy; 2026 Fabien Brocklesby</p>
					<p class="site-footer__note">
						The official personal website of Fabien Brocklesby
					</p>
				</div>
			</footer>
		</div>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
